gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: This line data layer represents roads for Douglas County, Wisconsin in 2015. [Refinement of dataset ready for Network Analyst and routing 1-13-2011 RJ. City of Superior, Douglas County and Forestry gas tax road Centerline datasets merged together to create a countywide feature class. Also included are the COS Snow Routes and COS Truck Routes, both of these routes have a field of data that gives their designation.]

gmd:purpose.gco:CharacterString: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Comprehensive County Centerline data]
